content.text: *Eye to Eye* is a single-screen action platformer that attempts to add to the conversation within the genre, but is also a meditation on personal struggles Austin has gone through in the past year. Processing pain, growth, and redemption through the wonderful creative endeavor that is game design.

He is a cinematographer who has shot several feature-length and short films as well as commercials, documentaries, and music videos. He's also had a passion for video games and an interest in game design for years and has decided to finally take the plunge beyond his Super Mario Maker roots to make his first game with Eye to Eye.
